title.value: [Plates to Allgemeine auf Geschichte und Erfahrung gegründete theoretisch-practische Wasserbaukunst.]

structuredValue.value: Wiebeking, Carl Friedrich von
Conrad, Frederik Willem

form.value: 97 items: copperplate engraving, on sheets 52 x 72 cm

note.value: Maps and drawings pertaining to hydraulic engineering in Europe and North America, predominantly in the Netherlands and Germany.
Relief shown pictorially or with hachures. Depth shown with soundings.
Plates may be from several different editions.
Bracketed information supplied by cataloger. Some plate titles derived from plate descriptions in books.
Some plates are in German, others in French.
